<plot>An enjoyable story of a 13-year-old girl, Louise (Anna Jones), who lives alone with her widowed mother (Helen Lindsay). Louise is sent off to a boarding school, but not before she discovers some secret documents kept hidden by her father. A curious look reveals that her father was a member of the secret order of Freemasons. When she finally gets to school, she tries to explain to her friends what the Freemasons are. Later, Louise's mother discovers a box of condoms in her daughter's room and wrongly presumes that the girl is sexually active. SECRETS was originally made for a British television series entitled "First Love".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?483793</url></doc>
